author: cmpilato
msg: Ensure that all paths printed from 'svn status' are relative-ized.
Prior to this change, modified items in external working copies were
used to transform the status path and moved-to/moved-from paths
into something relative to the current working directory.

author: tongfin
msg: Remove unused classes from Deployment Descriptor Editor plugin
The "uimaj-ep-runtime-deployeditor" plugin cannot be removed since it extends the UIMA parsing capabilities and it must be the fragment of the UIMA runtime plugin.
I will remove unused classes from the "uimaj-ep-runtime-deployeditor" plugin.
